videos.headline: South Carolina throws interception on opening drive

videos.description: South Florida's Quinton Flowers rushes in for 4-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Flowers scampers in for USF touchdown

videos.description: South Florida's Quinton Flowers scrambles out of the pocket and finds the edge for a 4-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: USF's Flowers scrambles for wild touchdown

videos.description: South Carolina's Steven Montac forces the fumble in the red zone, and the Gamecocks recover.
videos.headline: South Carolina's defense forces fumble in red zone

videos.description: South Carolina TE Hayden Hurst makes a great one-handed grab and scores for a 25-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: South Carolina's Hurst makes great one-handed catch for TD

videos.description: South Florida's Quinton Flowers takes it into the end zone himself to extend Bulls' lead.
videos.headline: USF's Flowers strolls into the end zone for TD

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (USF's Flowers strolls into the end zone for TD) 2016/12/29

videos.description: South Carolina RB Rico Dowdle grabs the poor snap and converts for a first down.
videos.headline: South Carolina turns bad snap into first down

videos.description: South Carolina's Jake Bentley connects with Deebo Samuel for a 3-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Bentley's TD pass cuts into South Florida's lead

videos.description: Quinton Flowers finds D'Ernest Johnson for a 37-yard touchdown with seven seconds remaining in the half.
videos.headline: USF pads lead with 37-yard TD before half

videos.description: South Florida's interim head coach T.J. Weist talks about dealing with RB injuries.
videos.headline: USF interim coach on dealing with RB injuries

videos.description: South Carolina's Rico Dowdle runs for a 26-yard gain before being knocked over by teammate.
videos.headline: South Carolina starts 2nd half with 26-yard run up the middle

videos.description: South Carolina WR Deebo Samuel takes the handoff and dives into the end zone for a 4-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: South Carolina WR takes sweep in for TD

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (South Carolina WR takes sweep in for TD) 2016/12/29

videos.description: South Florida's Tajee Fullwood intercepts the pass and returns it for a 47-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: USF extends lead with pick-six

videos.description: USF's Jaymon Thomas forces a fumble at the goal line and the Bulls' recover.
videos.headline: USF forces fumble on the goal line

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (USF forces fumble on the goal line) 2016/12/29

videos.description: South Carolina's Bryson Allen-Williams makes the diving, one-handed interception.
videos.headline: South Carolina makes incredible one-handed interception

videos.description: Jake Bentley completes a 31-yard pass to Bryan Edwards with a flea-flicker.
videos.headline: South Carolina uses flea-flicker for big gain

videos.description: South Carolina's Bryan Edwards makes a beautiful diving catch in the end zone.
videos.headline: Edwards makes great TD catch for South Carolina

videos.description: South Carolina wide receiver Bryan Edwards makes a diving touchdown catch after the ball deflects off the hands a South Florida defensive back.
videos.headline: Edwards makes diving TD grab after ball deflects off USF defender

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Edwards makes diving TD grab after ball deflects off USF defender) 2016/12/29

videos.description: Tajee Fullwood forces a fumble and South Florida once again recovers it in the end zone.
videos.headline: USF forces another red zone turnover

videos.description: South Carolina's Jonathan Hernandez returns the punt 39 yards to give them great field position.
videos.headline: South Carolina just misses punt return for TD

videos.description: A.J. Turner runs it in for the 1-yard touchdown, and Jake Bentley throws it to Hayden Hurst for the two-point conversion, tying South Carolina with USF.
videos.headline: South Carolina ties game with TD and 2-point conversion

videos.description: Quinton Flowers completes a pass to Elkanah Dillon for a 25-yard touchdown to give South Florida a 46-39 lead over South Carolina.
videos.headline: USF scores 1st TD in OT

videos.description: Jake Bentley is sacked by Mike Love and fumbles the ball. South Florida recovers it, winning the Birmingham Bowl in the process.
videos.headline: USF's defense stops South Carolina on 4th Down to win Birmingham Bowl

videos.description: South Carolina rallies late to send the game to overtime, but Quinton Flowers throws a 25-yard touchdown pass to Elkanah Dillon to give South Florida a 46-39 victory in the Birmingham Bowl.
videos.headline: USF prevails in OT to win Birmingham Bowl
